title: Subgraph of pango XA: (39 samples, 39 shown)
preamble: XA traces to a very clean recombination node, with no important reversions etc. Note that the causal sample (which triggers the initial recombination) is very close to the recombination event, and therefore lacks C8090T which is one of the "XA consensus" mutations (identified as those shared by over 90% of XA samples).
